creator: Mediar Team
descriptionHtml:
Currently QR scanning is no stranger to us. They are everywhere and the QR Code is used a lot in everyday life.



- Utilities provided by QR code:



✔️ Scan the bill payment.

✔️ Save on information exchange.

✔️ Pay with QR Pay.

✔️ Identify an item, a product.

✔️ Encrypt a lot of information like SMS, Call, Contact, GEO, Email ...

✔️ .....



- With QR codes you can use to make many gadgets or applications to life, with QR Tools we help you make those jobs become very simple:



✔️ Support you to scan QR codes and Barcode from your phone's camera.

✔️ Scan codes without an Internet connection.

✔️ Read QR's encrypted formats like SMS, Call, Contact, GEO, Email ...

✔️ Generate QR codes and Barcode by format and quickly.

✔️ Save your scanned history so you can manage them more easily.

✔️ You can save, share, copy .... scanned codes.

✔️ Scan QR codes from photos you have taken in your phone's memory or in gallery.

✔️ Easily create your own Barcode Scanner.

✔️ Find easy product information after scanning a code.



Hope to receive much support from you.



If you have any questions or requests, please contact us via gmail: phamngochoan23496@gmail.com



Thank you very much!

descriptionHtml:
All in one: QR & Barcode scanner app supports reading and creating QR and barcode with all formats, fastest, easy to use, and completely FREE!
QR Code Scanner app is the best app to generate, scan QR code and barcode for you.
✅ Free QR & Barcode scanner:
- Support scan QR codes or scan barcodes from both Cameras or from Photos on your phone.
- The application allows you to identify, scan QR code, scan barcodes from documents, SMS, phones, URLs, contacts, product information, ... and instantly display results with many different options for you.
- Support Flash in low light conditions.
- The application supports saving images of QR code or barcode for you to easily share with your friends or other social networks.
- An unlimited number of scans of QR codes or barcodes!
✅ Free QR & Barcode generate:
- Easily and quickly create QR or Barcode with many options: Text, Phone contact, SMS, URL, Email,...
- You can share the QR code, Barcode as soon as created.
- Unlimited creation of your QR or Barcode!
- The application does not require an internet connection for special QR or barcode codes.
The barcode scanner & QR code reader is really easy to use scan QR barcode scanner or barcode generator on your mobile device.
